reload_all_emos_libs

public String reload_all_emos_libs(in p1,
                                   in p2)
Reloads all EMOS libraries.

Parameters:
p1 - (in) 1 = load all as system modules 0 = load all as user modules [default = 0]
p2 - (in) 1 = close after load, do not animate 0 = leave open after load, animate [default = 0]
Returns:
E_OK: success !E_OK: failure

unload_all_emos_libs

public String unload_all_emos_libs()
